descriptionHtml:
Details
______________________
Of course you know what this mod does, it\'s just a save file.
If you want Ulrik like in the pic you MUST download this mod: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2488
And don\'t mind the skills, they\'re a bit overpowered, nothing that the console cant handle.

Installation
______________________
Just drop the file in your skyrim\\saves folder, in My Documents.

Credits
______________________
Chris57 - For his superb textures
